---
// TimeComparison.astro - Section comparaison temps DIY vs FormFlow
---

<section class="overflow-hidden bg-base-25">
  <div class="px-8 py-24 mx-auto md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-7xl">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-red-100 text-red-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
          ⏰ Time Reality Check
        </span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl/snug leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-2xl/snug md:text-3xl/snug lg:text-4xl/snug mt-4 font-semibold text-base-900">
        How Much Time Are You Really Wasting on Contact Forms?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base leading-normal mt-4 text-base-500 font-medium">
        Most WordPress site owners spend 15+ hours per month on manual form management. Here's the brutal breakdown:
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Time Comparison -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        
        <!-- DIY Approach - Time Wasters -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white ring-1 ring-red-200 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 9v3.75m9-.75a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9 3.75h.008v.008H12v-.008z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base-900">The DIY Nightmare</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-red-600 font-medium">15+ hours/month wasted</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Time Breakdown -->
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <!-- Email Sorting -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-red-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">1</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-base-900">Sorting Gmail Chaos</h4>
                    <span class="text-red-600 font-bold text-sm">4h/month</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-base-600 mb-3">
                    <em>"Where's that important inquiry from last Tuesday? Was it spam or real?"</em>
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-xs text-base-500 space-y-1">
                    <div>• 20 min/day digging through emails</div>
                    <div>• Missing important inquiries in spam</div>
                    <div>• No organization system</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Manual Spam Filtering -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-red-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">2</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-base-900">Fighting Spam Manually</h4>
                    <span class="text-red-600 font-bold text-sm">3h/month</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-base-600 mb-3">
                    <em>"Another 'Make $5000/week' message... Delete, delete, delete."</em>
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-xs text-base-500 space-y-1">
                    <div>• 15 min/day deleting obvious spam</div>
                    <div>• Accidentally deleting real inquiries</div>
                    <div>• No smart filtering</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- WordPress Admin Dance -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-red-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">3</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-base-900">WordPress Admin Juggling</h4>
                    <span class="text-red-600 font-bold text-sm">2.5h/month</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-base-600 mb-3">
                    <em>"Let me check WPForms... wait, was it in the dashboard or emails?"</em>
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-xs text-base-500 space-y-1">
                    <div>• Jumping between admin and email</div>
                    <div>• No centralized view</div>
                    <div>• Losing context constantly</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Manual Response Management -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-red-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">4</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-base-900">Response Chaos</h4>
                    <span class="text-red-600 font-bold text-sm">3h/month</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-base-600 mb-3">
                    <em>"Did I already reply to this? What did I tell them before?"</em>
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-xs text-base-500 space-y-1">
                    <div>• No conversation history</div>
                    <div>• Duplicating responses</div>
                    <div>• Slow manual typing</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Analysis & Follow-up -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-red-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-red-500">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">5</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-base-900">Manual Tracking & Follow-ups</h4>
                    <span class="text-red-600 font-bold text-sm">2.5h/month</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-base-600 mb-3">
                    <em>"I should probably follow up on that quote request... when was that?"</em>
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-xs text-base-500 space-y-1">
                    <div>• No lead priority system</div>
                    <div>• Missing follow-up opportunities</div>
                    <div>• Zero insights or analytics</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Total Waste -->
              <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-red-100 rounded-lg border-2 border-red-300">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-base-900">Total Time Wasted:</span>
                  <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">15+ hours/month</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-red-700 mt-2">
                  <strong>That's 180+ hours per year</strong> - nearly a full work month!
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FormFlow Approach -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white ring-1 ring-green-200 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base-900">The FormFlow Way</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-green-600 font-medium">2 hours/month maximum</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Automated Solutions -->
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <!-- AI Inbox -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-green-500">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-base-900">AI-Organized Inbox</h4>
                    <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm">30s/day</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-base-600 mb-3">
                    <em>"All my inquiries, perfectly organized and prioritized. Finally."</em>
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-xs text-base-500 space-y-1">
                    <div>• ✅ Auto-categorized by urgency</div>
                    <div>• ✅ Instant sentiment analysis</div>
                    <div>• ✅ Professional unified inbox</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Smart Spam Detection -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-green-500">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5 0a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-base-900">99.9% Spam Blocked</h4>
                    <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm">0 min/day</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-base-600 mb-3">
                    <em>"I never see spam anymore. AI handles everything."</em>
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-xs text-base-500 space-y-1">
                    <div>• ✅ AI learns your preferences</div>
                    <div>• ✅ Zero false positives</div>
                    <div>• ✅ Focus on real inquiries only</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Seamless Integration -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-green-500">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-base-900">WordPress Native</h4>
                    <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm">5 min setup</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-base-600 mb-3">
                    <em>"One plugin. Everything works together perfectly."</em>
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-xs text-base-500 space-y-1">
                    <div>• ✅ Direct WPForms integration</div>
                    <div>• ✅ Single dashboard for everything</div>
                    <div>• ✅ No more tool juggling</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Smart Responses -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-green-500">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-base-900">AI-Powered Responses</h4>
                    <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm">2 min/response</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-base-600 mb-3">
                    <em>"Smart templates, full conversation history. Professional every time."</em>
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-xs text-base-500 space-y-1">
                    <div>• ✅ Response suggestions</div>
                    <div>• ✅ Complete conversation threads</div>
                    <div>• ✅ Professional templates</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Analytics & Insights -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-green-500">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-base-900">Automatic Analytics</h4>
                    <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm">0 min setup</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-base-600 mb-3">
                    <em>"I see exactly which inquiries matter most. Data-driven decisions."</em>
                  </p>
                  <div class="text-xs text-base-500 space-y-1">
                    <div>• ✅ Lead scoring & prioritization</div>
                    <div>• ✅ Response time tracking</div>
                    <div>• ✅ Conversion insights</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Total Time Saved -->
              <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-green-100 rounded-lg border-2 border-green-300">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-base-900">Total Time Investment:</span>
                  <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600">2 hours/month</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-green-700 mt-2">
                  <strong>Save 13+ hours every month.</strong> That's 156+ hours per year back in your life!
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Time Saved Badge -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-16 h-16 bg-accent-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
